---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — NM Nonprofits"
  description="NM Nonprofits is the definitive directory of New Mexico nonprofits, foundations, and grant opportunities."
>
  <div class="container-content py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About NM Nonprofits</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      The definitive directory of New Mexico's social sector — built to connect communities with the organizations that serve them.
    </p>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-10">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">What we are</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          NM Nonprofits is a comprehensive, searchable directory of nonprofit organizations, foundations, and funders operating in New Mexico. We index 501(c)(3) public charities, community foundations, tribal nonprofits, fiscal sponsors, and the philanthropic institutions that support them.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Our goal is simple: make it easy to find the organizations doing the most important work in New Mexico — whether you're a donor, a grantseeker, a journalist, a researcher, or a community member looking for help.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">What we cover</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Nonprofit organizations across all 33 New Mexico counties</li>
          <li>Community foundations and private funders</li>
          <li>Open grant opportunities for NM nonprofits</li>
          <li>Sector-by-sector issue area browsing</li>
          <li>City and regional filters</li>
          <li>Events, trainings, and professional development resources</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Get listed</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Basic listings are free. If your organization isn't in the directory yet, you can submit it through our listing form. Premium tiers offer enhanced visibility, grant-matching alerts, and a dedicated profile page with additional details.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <a href="/submit/" class="btn-primary">Submit Your Organization</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Contact us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Questions, corrections, or partnership inquiries? Reach us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@nmnonprofits.com" class="text-turquoise-700 hover:underline">hello@nmnonprofits.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
